OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with warm sunny spells.
OL,7,FStaying dry with lengthy clear spells
OL,8,Fovernight. Breezy along the north Kent
OL,9,Fcoast, otherwise, light winds. A
OL,10,Fcooler night for many, compared to
OL,11,Frecent nights.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAreas of cloud for the morning
OL,14,Fand at first in the afternoon, then
OL,15,Fmost places gradually becoming sunny.
OL,16,FRather warm for most places, highest
OL,17,Ftemperatures across Hampshire.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
