OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FRemaining warm with light winds and
OL,7,Fdry. Possibly cloudy at times Monday
OL,8,Fand Tuesday, then Wednesday sunnier
OL,9,Fconditions are likely.
